column5: I am looking for specific tackle taht is not sold at BPS.  I seem to recall someone saying there is another shop near BPS.  I know about the one on the highway called Fish-Onatio but I think there is another.  If you know the name and location that would be very helpful.  Thanks
It might be this one Cudz, I've been there.  Its not a huge store, but it has some cool stuff.  Angling Specialties Link  Joey
Thnks I will give them a call
Give Angling Specialties a visit, a lot of float fishing guys on the forum go there.
You are probally talking about JB's fishing depot. Very close to there.
JB is all the why down on the 401 west of 400, not close at all.
